title: Sucholaski
text:
Sucholaski () is a <a href="village">village</a> in the administrative district of <a href="Gmina%20Wydminy">Gmina Wydminy</a>, within <a href="Gi%C5%BCycko%20County">Giżycko County</a>, <a href="Warmian-Masurian%20Voivodeship">Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship</a>, in northern Poland. 
It lies approximately north-west of <a href="Wydminy">Wydminy</a>, east of <a href="Gi%C5%BCycko">Giżycko</a>, and east of the regional capital <a href="Olsztyn">Olsztyn</a>.
